The HQ also accepts [[nl/Manual/Base Set/Cargos/Passagiers|passagiers]] en [[nl/Manual/Base Set/Cargos/Post|post]] delivered to it as well as providing a limited amount of passengers and mail itself. During an [[nl/Manual/Economie#recessie|economische recessie]] there's only half of the usual amount.

As the HQ shows your success, it is common for players to build them as centerpieces of the transport empire, usually atop a large, artificial mountain, or on an island in the sea. It is common to see millions spent on such large areas.

There are various different [[en/Manual/NewGRF]]s available if you don't like your HQ design, or it being dwarfed by other buildings in a town.
